DarkWind has a daily rewards system that will reward a player
with anything from experience and gold to interesting items.

Items are claimable once every 24 hrs via the |YKB'daily' |YKOcommand.
After claiming a new 24 hr lockout starts followed by a 24 hr
claim period. They are not claimable by calendar day and do
require a player be active for 30 mins prior to claiming.

Registered multies share one daily streak. Any registered multi can
claim the shared daily reward after that character has been active for
30 minutes, and the reward items go to the character who runs |YKBdaily|YKO.

